name: parsl-split
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "parsl" %}
{% set version = "1.2.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "342c74ee39fa210d74b8adfb455f0a9c20d9f059ec5bd9d60c5bdc9929abcdcc" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}-split
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/Parsl/{{ name }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6

outputs:
  - name: {{ name }}
    script: install_parsl.sh
    build:
      noarch: python
      entry_points:
        - parsl-globus-auth = parsl.data_provider.globus:cli_run

    requirements:
      host:
        - python >=3.6
        - pip
      run:
        - python >=3.6
        # requirements.txt
        - pyzmq >=17.1.2
        - typeguard >=2.10
        - typing-extensions
        - globus-sdk
        - dill
        - tblib
        - requests
        - paramiko
        - psutil >=5.5.1

    test:
      requires:
        - pip
      imports:
        - parsl
      commands:
        - pip check

  - name: {{ name }}-with-monitoring
    build:
      noarch: python
    requirements:
      host:
        - python >=3.6
      run:
        - python >=3.6
        - {{ pin_subpackage(name, max_pin='x.x.x.x.x.x') }}
        - sqlalchemy >=1.3.0,!=1.3.4,<1.4
        - sqlalchemy-utils
        - pydot
        - networkx
        - flask >=1.0.2
        - flask-sqlalchemy
        - pandas
        - plotly
        - python-daemon
    test:
      imports:
        - parsl
        - parsl.monitoring
      commands:
        - pip check
      requires:
        - pip

  - name: {{ name }}-with-aws
    build:
      noarch: python
    requirements:
      host:
        - python >=3.6
      run:
        - python >=3.6
        - {{ pin_subpackage(name, max_pin='x.x.x.x.x.x') }}
        - boto3
    test:
      imports:
        - parsl
      commands:
        - pip check
      requires:
        - pip

  - name: {{ name }}-with-kubernetes
    build:
      noarch: python
    requirements:
      host:
        - python >=3.6
      run:
        - python >=3.6
        - {{ pin_subpackage(name, max_pin='x.x.x.x.x.x') }}
        - kubernetes
    test:
      imports:
        - parsl
      commands:
        - pip check
      requires:
        - pip
